                <img src="/img/placeholders/avatar-10.png" />
            </div>
            <div class="name">Matt Mathew</div>
        </div>
        <div class="details">
            <div>I would love to be able to choose an importing frame-rate that the system would automatically interpolate the fbx into. Sometimes I get models encoded in various frame-rates, and its always a pain to interpolate them one by one.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

